      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The exterior has some minor dings and the paint is fading in a few spots, while the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery. It runs well, but a buyer should expect to address some upcoming maintenance items like brake pads and a minor oil leak in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone looking for affordable transportation.",
