    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project with plenty of potential? This vehicle is ready for a dedicated owner to roll up their sleeves and bring it back to life! While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic, budget-friendly opportunity for a DIY enthusiast or anyone looking for a solid parts car. Grab this diamond in the rough and make it your own!",
